ws\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's tugged on viewers' heartstrings, with Livie sharing on X: 'Four minutes into Simone Biles' Netflix series and I am already so emotional.'\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"viewers' heartstrings\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"Livie sharing\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"Four minutes\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another shared: 'I am not even halfway thru episode 1 of Simone Biles: Rising documentary on Netflix, and I am in tears'.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5609859074049003e-15, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The critics were impressed by the documentary too, rating it a perfect 100% on review aggregator site Rotten Tomatoes.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1507, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotten_Tomatoes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rotten Tomatoes\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotten_Tomatoes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotten_Tomatoes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The critics\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"the documentary\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anmar Kalia, writing for the Observer, said: 'Packed as it is with jaw-dropping slow-motion footage of Biles's vaults and leaps, it's impossible to come away from Rising without rooting for this astounding woman, who has dominated her sport for a decade.'\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anmar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anmar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anmar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anmar\"}, {\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.578612033148332e-14, \"text\": \"Kalia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalya\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Observer\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"jaw-dropping slow-motion footage\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles's vaults\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"leaps\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"this astounding woman\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"a decade\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Robert Lloyd of the Los Angeles Times calls it 'A genuinely inspiring two-part documentary.'\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Lloyd_(bass)\", \"score\": 0.4273712031787774, \"rank\": 0.6912162162160294, \"text\": \"Robert Lloyd\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Lloyd_(bass)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Lloyd_(bass)\"}, {\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1830, \"ti